snippet.title: Official Destiny Expansion I: The Dark Below Trailer
snippet.description:
Expand your Destiny adventure with new weapons, armor, and gear, and increase your light level in The Dark Below. Play through new story missions, dominate in three new PvP Crucible arenas, or join friends to take on co-op challenges -- including a new Strike and brand-new six-player Raid. 

Pre-order The Dark Below at destinythegame.com and receive the EV-30 Tumbler Sparrow.* http://www.destinythegame.com/wheretobuy?bundle=expansionPass

Destiny Expansion I: The Dark Below release date subject to change.  Destiny game required to play, sold separately.

*Destiny Expansion Pass or Destiny Expansion I: The Dark Below must be purchased and redeemed by January 15, 2015 to receive the EV-30 Tumbler Sparrow. If you have already purchased Destiny Expansion Pass or Destiny Expansion I: The Dark Below, the EV-30 Tumbler Sparrow is available before or starting on December 9, 2014. See http://www.destinythegame.com/wheretobuy/tumbler-sparrow for further details.
